R. O. CHENEY v. STATE OF FLORIDA 17 So. (2nd) 122

January Term, 1944

February 29, 1944 En Banc C. A. Avriett, for appellant. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, and John G. Wynn, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Affirmed on authority of Scott v. State, 138 Fla. 568, 189 So. 661.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, THOMAS, ADAMS and SE-BRING, JJ., concur. BROWN, J., dissents. CHAPMAN, J., not participating.
